title: UK welcomes strong African Union leadership on Burundi (FCO - UK Foreign and Commonwealth Office) ...
text: ( Source : FCO - UK Foreign and Commonwealth Office ) The UK government welcomes the African Union 's Peace and Security Council 's statement on Burundi . We support actions by the African Union Commission to ensure a dialogue is convened
